        "caption_j8ndmz": {
          "type": "caption",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "Welcome, Higher Ed Heroes!",
            "text_style": "caption-with-letter-spacing",
            "text_size": "medium"
          }
        },
        "text_9nTUEN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Whether you’re in operations, procurement, housing, IT, admissions, marketing, sports or just got “voluntold” to manage ID accessories for campus events—this guide is for you.</p><p>We know ordering badge reels, holders, and lanyards isn't glamorous. But when thousands of students, faculty, and staff need visible, durable IDs, getting this right matters. That’s why we created this guide—to make your job easier, your process smoother, and your choice defensible (without needing a committee).</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
